{"tid":1447413,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日812 全世界同我入機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:04:30.000Z","uid":22717,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"96e02292fba0ea464c6cab9c167b406ad92f7479","tid":1447413,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"街頭勇武好明顯已經到哂樽頸位<br />\n今日狗扮示威者真係無從入手 諗唔到點拆<br />\n繼續落去只會損失更多勇武手足<br />\n<br />\n而機場升級係唯一手段<br />\n唔係要去衝禁區唔係去破壞<br />\n而係去<span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場運作</span><br />\n依2日都有入一入機場 發覺只係達到宣傳效果<br />\n但好多人其實都係齋坐嗌口號<br />\n<br />\n但其實我唔洗一定要跟規矩坐<br />\n上離境大堂坐又得 得閒推下車仔又得<br />\n想去旅行但冇買機票去櫃位個邊阻下又得<br />\n所有你地諗到可以阻止機場運作既野都可以做<br />\n最理想係好似泰國咁佔領控制塔 依個係比較難<br />\n但人多就一定可以癱瘓機場運作<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再抱有會阻住旅客既包袱<br />\n國難當前 唔理得咁多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日812 全世界同我入機場</span><br />\n<br />\n利申香城online"},{"pid":"26b35ecae2e4206c988c2196d862b84af955b943","tid":1447413,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"P1"},{"pid":"4ea558350ceca4aeb857b679522d7b3dd4d97963","tid":1447413,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"P2"},{"pid":"fde6c4bf8eabe72b5543ce1b63cc0e332b7a1500","tid":1447413,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"P3"},{"pid":"065ef020a616cb67541047f32873eaacdac01c2c","tid":1447413,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2917db4f85290daac95280c11a18384bdb0d30e","tid":1447413,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:33.000Z","msg":"P4"},{"pid":"89d493ae52068f57c1b5d8055a2b4bb0fa9c2202","tid":1447413,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"P5"},{"pid":"b61e33bac97ef9ece2f065